{
  "id": "adv_event_2205_01_04",
  "title": "本当に\nやりたいこと",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "私、が……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What about me…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 2.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "うん……\n今のお姉ちゃん、全然キラキラしてない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah…\nOnee-chan right now‚ you're not shining at all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.0666666667,
      "endTime": 8.0330613772,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "千紗。……どういうこと？\nちゃんと説明してちょうだい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa… What do you mean?\nPlease explain properly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.4,
      "endTime": 14.1183673857,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんは、ずっと\n私のことを立てようとしてくれてる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Onee-chan has always been\ntrying to support me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.3333333333,
      "endTime": 18.9791385015,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "それがユニットのためだって言うけど……\nそれなら、お姉ちゃんはどうしてそんなに辛そうなの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She says it's for the sake of the team…\nBut then‚ why does Onee-chan look so troubled?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.1666666667,
      "endTime": 27.352494351100002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "私だって……いつまでもお姉ちゃんに支えられなくても\n一人でも大丈夫だから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even if I can't always rely on Onee-chan forever‚\nI'll be fine on my own.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.5666666667,
      "endTime": 34.846096592900004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "私にも……お姉ちゃんを支えさせて？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let me support Onee-chan too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.2,
      "endTime": 39.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "千紗……で、でも、私は……お姉ちゃんだから\nあなたを、支えないと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa… B-but‚ I'm… your Onee-chan‚ so…\nI have to support you…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.9333333333,
      "endTime": 49.6770064672,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "（あ……お姉ちゃん、辛そう……）\n（でも、ここでやめたら、私達、前に進めない……！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Ah… Onee-chan looks troubled…)\n(But if we stop here‚ we won't be able to move forward…!)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.8666666667,
      "endTime": 60.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "こ、このままお姉ちゃんが譲っちゃうなら……\n私が、ほんとに前に出ちゃうんだから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I'll step forward for real\nif Onee-chan is going to give up…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.9333333333,
      "endTime": 69.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "ち、千紗……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ch-Chisa…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.2333333333,
      "endTime": 70.93151930169999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "私ばっかり目立っちゃうよ！　それでも……いいの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll end up overshadowing you! Is that… okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.1333333333,
      "endTime": 77.0488433202,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "それ、は……でも、私は……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… but I…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.2666666667,
      "endTime": 82.1239910762,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃん……\nお姉ちゃんが本当にやりたいことはなんなの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Onee-chan…\nWhat is it that you really want to do?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.3333333333,
      "endTime": 88.6333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "私の……本当にやりたいこと……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What I… truly want to do…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.8666666667,
      "endTime": 92.9448980491,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "今のお姉ちゃんは自分を殺してると思う\nこれじゃあバトルだって勝てないし、何より……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think our current Onee-chan is killing herself.\nWe won't win battles like this‚ and above all…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.1333333333,
      "endTime": 102,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04-chs011.m4a",
      "text": "私は……そんなお姉ちゃん、見たくないよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't want to see Onee-chan like this…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.2333333333,
      "endTime": 107.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04-chs012.m4a",
      "text": "月ストのお姉ちゃんも好きだけど\n私はこのユニットで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I love the Onee-chan from Moon Tempest‚ but…\nIn this team…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.6666666667,
      "endTime": 112.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04-chs013.m4a",
      "text": "小学生の時、私の前でアイドルの真似をして見せて\nくれてた時の、キラキラしたお姉ちゃんがまた見たい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to see the sparkling Onee-chan\nwho imitated idols in front of me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.1,
      "endTime": 122.74225792850001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04-chs014.m4a",
      "text": "好きなことを自由にやって、楽しそうなお姉ちゃんに\nまた……会いたいよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And the Onee-chan who enjoys doing what she loves‚\nI want to see her again…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.0666666667,
      "endTime": 130.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "千紗……ごめんね、ありがとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa… I'm sorry‚ thank you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.3333333333,
      "endTime": 137.89723361330002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04-chs015.m4a",
      "text": "ううん……私こそ、ごめんね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No… I should be the one saying sorry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.4,
      "endTime": 142.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "私の、本当にやりたいこと……か",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What is it… that I truly want to do…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.0666666667,
      "endTime": 147.6814964931,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04-chs016.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんは私や月ストの\nみんなを立てようとしてくれるけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Onee-chan‚ you've always been trying to\nsupport me and Moon Tempest…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.9333333333,
      "endTime": 153.9533331236,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04-chs017.m4a",
      "text": "本当は……お姉ちゃんも、センターに立ちたいんじゃ\nないのかなって……ずっと思ってたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But deep down… I wondered if Onee-chan\nalso wanted to be the center…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.1666666667,
      "endTime": 162.76666666659997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "私が……センターに？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Me… as the center…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163,
      "endTime": 166.88866214749999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04-chs018.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんは、歌って踊ってみんなの視線を\n釘付けにするキラキラしたアイドルに憧れて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Onee-chan‚ you admired idols who\nsing and dance‚ captivating everyone…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.1,
      "endTime": 175.25306119919998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04-chs019.m4a",
      "text": "あんなに家族で話し合ってまで\nアイドルになったんだよ、覚えてる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even we discuss this at the family talk‚\nyou became an idol for that reason… Do you remember?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 175.4666666667,
      "endTime": 180.93333333340001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "もちろんよ\nあの時は……いろいろと大変だったっけ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ I do.\nThat time… it was quite challenging.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 181.1333333333,
      "endTime": 186.7584127745,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04-chs020.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんは真面目でなんでも出来るから\nみんなを支えることが多くなってたのかなって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think because Onee-chan is reliable and capable of anything‚\nYou ended up supporting everyone more and more.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 186.9666666667,
